details:
PhotoPrint is a utility offering special features for printing digital
 photographs and other images.  It can print multiple images on a
 single page, create posters split over several pages, arrange images
 into a sort of carousel when printing on CDs, adding fading or
 decorative borders to images, etc.  It also supports use of ICC colour
 profiles and sending 16-bit data to the printer.
 works-with::image
